title: Extinction v1.0.4.1
description:
Trippy the Triceratop's survival is at stake. Help him escape extinction by DODGING asteroids, OUTRUNNING meteor showers, WEAVING through caves, and COLLECTING gems to buy evolutions!

This fun and addictive 3rd person endless runner features: 
- Progress through themed grassland, desert and apocalypse zones 
- Simple easy-to-use controls 
- Unique power-ups 
- Outstanding 3D graphics 
- Exciting endless gameplay 
- Challenging achievements

Stay tuned for regular FREE updates with new achievements, evolutions and mechanics!
'Join Trippy and DODGE asteroids, SURVIVE rains of fire, WEAVE through dark caves, and EVOLVE a variety of upgrades, all in a desperate bid to ESCAPE EXTINCTION!'
